Beyonce, 40, left fans stunned with the jaw-dropping artwork for her highly anticipated album, Renaissance.The mum-of-three stripped naked with just strategically placed metalwork covering her modesty while she sat on a horse.The iconic singer even treated fans to a rare caption and explained that the album allowed her to feel “free and adventurous” during a “scary time for the world”.She added that she hopes her music will make fans feel “unique, strong and sexy”.Fans were sent into a frenzy, with @bawbawmisses writing: “OKAY QUEEN OF THE WORLD.”Morgan echoed: “Whew my heart dropped.”And Rob exclaimed: “We needed a warning!!!”